    <objectives>
      <material>
        <mattext texttype="text/html">&lt;h1&gt;Session 1 Quiz – Variables, Data Types, and Operators&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Test your understanding of JavaScript variables, primitive data types, and basic operators.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Topics Covered:&lt;/strong&gt;
- let, const, and var declarations
- Primitive data types (string, number, boolean, null, undefined)
- Arithmetic and comparison operators
- Type coercion
- Variable naming conventions&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instructions:&lt;/strong&gt;
- 16 questions from the Session 1 question bank
- 20 minute time limit
- 3 attempts allowed
- 16 points total (1 point per question)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;After syncing the question bank to Canvas:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</mattext>
      </material>
    </objectives>
